#, fuzzy
msgid "If a class is annotated with `@Startup` but with no scope annotation then `@ApplicationScoped` is added automatically."
msgstr "如果一个类标注了 `@Startup` 注解但未标注作用域注解，则会自动添加 `@ApplicationScoped` 注解。"

